short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a button to view logs from fflogs in xivanlysis.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds enhancements to fflogs, allowing quick access to all logs in xivanalysis.

Adds a button next to the tabs in your fflogs reports to quickly and easily open in xivanalysis. 

Quickly open reports filtered by fight or by player with one click.
